Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.93,0:51:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿（20点17分涉谷区 按摩店按摩室）
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.84,0:51:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿这里好胀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.78,0:51:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿失礼了 请问换好衣服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.53,0:51:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿是的 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.78,0:51:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿是吗 那就失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.28,0:51:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿六十分钟的服务 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.80,0:51:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.89,0:51:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那就趴下来可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.27,0:51:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿身体放松一些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.37,0:51:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.04,0:51:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那就失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.89,0:51:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿帮你疏通血液
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.93,0:52:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.38,0:52:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那个
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.92,0:52:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我以为是女性按摩师
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.89,0:52:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你预约的没有指定按摩师
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.03,0:52:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿现在这个时间是我担当
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.28,0:52:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.37,0:52:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.94,0:52:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我们还有其他客人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.86,0:52:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿都预约满了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.38,0:52:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.35,0:52:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.28,0:52:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿如果痛就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.51,0:52:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿先从脚部开始按摩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.41,0:52:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.28,0:52:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.40,0:52:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.62,0:53:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那我帮你舒展一下
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.87,0:53:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿很胀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.27,0:53:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.83,0:53:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿很痛吗
Comment: 0,0:53:33.47,0:53:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,***
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.37,0:53:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那个
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.05,0:53:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿不要摸这里
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.96,0:53:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.97,0:53:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿这里很多淋巴需要疏通的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.37,0:53:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿不按摩那里吗
